channel.description:
Hey guys once again im here to ask you another question that i hope u can answer with your mighty wisdom.
some of my teleports case files are missing, Varrock Lumbridge Camelot WatchTower and trollheim, can some please tell me what the cases are for theese files, because i have loooked all over the file and have found no sign of them...

item.title: Case Files (Clicking Most) 317
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

Koolvin:

Try clicking the teleport, then looking at the cmd prompt.

That will only work if there is a println in case 185.

So to add on to what he said, look in Client.java and search
case 185:
Under that you may or may not see

if(playerName.equalsIgnoreCase("SomeonesUsername...")){ println("ab=" + actionButtonId); }

Replace the SomeonesUsername… with your username, compile and than check the cmd prompt when you click the teleports.
